{"tid":664553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢中啊叔讓座俾支那女，支女唔領情。","createTime":"2018-05-14T07:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T13:56:31.000Z","uid":62011,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2ea4e3f5447c76993c7264c62eb554a8a965728a","tid":664553,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"頭先搭西鐵，隔離坐住個廢中。去到元朗站，有兩個支那女人推住架bb車入黎。個廢中即刻起身，仲要懶型咁用普通話講：你們坐。<br />\n<br />\n點知兩個支那人唔坐，其中一個西返個阿叔面。個阿叔個樣嬲撚到，谷住道氣。<br />\n<br />\n我見到都心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後附送支那女圖<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/152521_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F152521_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1975d25f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac6c6a534250186c817f9e08e6c5aa8ab151d3c3","tid":664553,"uid":158585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:30:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾廢中想叫免費雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e8fa2608c92a42151167ddea38dc8843297ffb","tid":664553,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"908ec63bfbfd54ef5e66a93c931e1617d6f8dba2","tid":664553,"uid":137921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"親中呀拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當你狗咋死廢中"},{"pid":"de4bbf2a408d947d4c5d56ef68d1256d6f45c8b9","tid":664553,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾 讓比d生蕃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}